Aspexi.text: Commission must be provided for of ---

Assensio.text: Compliments of the season to all from all here

Assequor.text: Comply with their requirements as far as you can

Assero.text: Comply with their requirements in all respects

Assessor.text: Comply with their requirements under protest

Assideo.text: Compromise, if you think it desirable

Associo.text: Conclude negotiations at once, or break off

Assolet.text: Have you come to any conclusion

Assuesco.text: Condole with you in our mutual great loss

Assulose.text: Condole with you in your great loss

Assulto.text: Confidential agent will be sent on our behalf

Astaphis.text: Congratulate you on the birth of a daughter

Asterion.text: Congratulate you on the birth of a son

Asterno.text: Congratulate you on the happy event
